description: Returns the names of all active (not deleted) resources.

parameters.name: pageToken
parameters.description: The token to advance to the next page of results from your request. To get a page token, perform an initial GetActiveNames request. If your results are paginated, the response will return a next page token that you can specify as the page token in a subsequent request.

nested_items.name: activeNames
nested_items.description: The list of active names returned by the get active names request.

nested_items.name: nextPageToken
nested_items.description: The token to advance to the next page of results from your request.
